divs: Sighting DetailsSighting Report: It looked like there were four small, circular objects in the sky, all changing different colours (colours included blue, yellow, orange and pink or purple, not sure). I was outside practicing baskbetball and when I saw it, I told my mom to come out and see it, but when she got there, they were gone. I thought it was nothing until my friend, Jarred, called and was completely freaking out and he said he d seen it too. Jarred reads books about UFOs all the time and said that these were like something out of the books so I Googled a UFO reporting site and you know the rest. The crafts seemed to make a sound that I could only hear outside of the house, too. It was very low pitched and almost sounded like "Loooo".
